Events.Name: Clash of Titans Key Contest
Events.Description: Collect and spend Clash of Titans Keys and Defeat Titans and Mini-Titans in Contests and Tours to earn amazing prizes for your Faction!
Events.EventMarqueeText: Collect and spend Clash of Titans Keys and Defeat Titans and Mini-Titans in Contests and Tours to earn amazing prizes for your Faction!

Defeat Ric Flair "Mini Titan" in the Clash of Titans Tour Book 2 - Sting Chapter Hell Mode!

Defeat Nia Jax "Titan" in the Titan Game Blitz #1 - Hell Mode!
Defeat Titus O'Neil "Titan" in the Titan Game Blitz #2 - Hell Mode!

Events.Name: Titan Game Blitz #1 Faction Event!
Events.Description: Defeat the Titan in Hell Mode to make progress in the Titan Game Blitz Faction Contest(s)! Earn Titan Ingots on your journey for a chance at massive Coin Prizes!
Events.EventMarqueeText: Defeat the Titan in Hell Mode to make progress in the Titan Game Blitz Faction Contest(s)! Earn Titan Ingots on your journey for a chance at massive Coin Prizes!

Events.Name: CLASH OF TITANS SHOWDOWN FACTION CONTEST
Events.Description: COMPETE AT THE HIGHEST LEVEL! EQUIP AND UPGRADE THE SHOWDOWN PERKS IN YOUR ROSTER SCREEN!
Events.EventMarqueeText: Compete in the CLASH OF TITANS SHOWDOWN alongside your Faction to win 6 MILLION Coins, 26 4-Star Silver tokens, and much more!

Events.Name: Clash of Titans Contest
Events.Description: Make progress by earning Clash of Titan Coins in Tours, Feud, Blitz, Faction, Showdown Tournaments and additional contests. Prizes include a chance to win a new Superstar, Daniel Bryan "The Planet's Champion", and many more valuable items!
Events.EventMarqueeText: Make progress by earning Clash of Titan Coins in Tours, Feud, Blitz, Faction, Showdown Tournaments and additional contests. Prizes include a chance to win a new Superstar, Daniel Bryan "The Planet's Champion", and many more valuable items!

Methods.Description: Spend 1 Clash of Titans Universal Turnbuckle
Increase the talent of Kofi Kingston "Against All Odds" by 1
Increase the talent of Fandango "Deputy Dango" by 1
Increase the talent of Tyler Breeze "Prince Pretty" by 1

Rewards.Reward: Daniel Bryan "The Planet's Champion" 1 Star Gold

Events.Name: CLASH OF TITANS SHOWDOWN SOLO CONTEST
Events.Description: COMPETE AT THE HIGHEST LEVEL! EQUIP AND UPGRADE THE SHOWDOWN PERKS IN YOUR ROSTER SCREEN!
Events.EventMarqueeText: Compete in the Clash of Titans SHOWDOWN for a chance to win Dusty Rhodes "The American Dream" at 4-Star Bronze, Showdown Coins, Clash of Titans Coins and much more!

Rewards.Reward: Dusty Rhodes "The American Dream" 4 Star Bronze
Dusty Rhodes "The American Dream" 3 Star Gold
Dusty Rhodes "The American Dream" 3 Star Gold
